---

<PageLayout
  title="Financial Institution Partnerships | HedgeFlows"
  description="Partner with HedgeFlows to give your SME and mid-market clients institutional-grade treasury, FX risk management, and cash management — without building it yourself."
>
  <Hero
    title="Better SME coverage, without building from scratch"
    subtitle="Banks and FX brokers know the SME opportunity is huge — but the economics of serving them with treasury, risk management, and cash solutions don't stack up. We change that. Partner with us to extend institutional-grade capabilities to your SME clients, on your terms."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Explore a Partnership', href: '/treasury-health-check' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'Email Our Team', href: 'mailto:partners@hedgeflows.com' }}
  >
    <PartnersScene slot="scene" partnerType="Financial Institutions" metricValue="5.5M" metricLabel="UK SMEs underserved on treasury" />
  </Hero>

  <TrustBar slider={true} />

  <!-- Awards & Regulation -->
  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-[#F8FAFB] border-y border-gray-100">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-0 md:divide-x md:divide-gray-200">
        <!-- TMI Awards 2025 -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 md:justify-center md:px-8">
          <img
            src="/assets/logos/clients/tmi.jpg"
            alt="TMI Awards 2025 for Innovation & Excellence"
            class="w-20 h-20 md:w-24 md:h-24 rounded-2xl object-cover flex-shrink-0"
          />
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-heading text-[1rem]">Best Risk Management</p>
            <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">TMI Awards 2025</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TTP Awards 2026 -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 md:justify-center md:px-8">
          <img
            src="/assets/logos/clients/ttp.jpg"
            alt="TTP Awards 2026"
            class="w-20 h-20 md:w-24 md:h-24 rounded-2xl object-cover flex-shrink-0"
          />
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-heading text-[1rem]">SME Inclusion Initiative</p>
            <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">TTP Awards 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FCA Badge -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 md:justify-center md:px-8">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 md:w-24 md:h-24 bg-brand-green-pale rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 text-brand-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-heading text-[1rem]">FCA Regulated</p>
            <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">Firm Reference Number: 1008699</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[#F8FAFB]">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">The SME treasury gap</h2>
        <p class="section-subheading mx-auto max-w-3xl">
          Mid-market and SME businesses are the backbone of international trade — but they're the most underserved segment when it comes to treasury and risk management
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16">
        {problemStats.map((stat) => (
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-brand-green leading-none mb-2">{stat.value}</p>
            <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed">{stat.label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Problem narrative -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-[1.125rem] font-bold text-text-heading mb-3">The challenge for banks</h3>
          <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed">
            Your corporate treasury desk serves large enterprises well — but the cost-to-serve model breaks down for SMEs. Building bespoke FX risk advisory, cash management tools, and hedging solutions for hundreds of smaller clients isn't viable. So they get a basic portal, a rate over the phone, and little guidance. Many drift to fintechs or brokers for FX — and you lose the relationship.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-[1.125rem] font-bold text-text-heading mb-3">The challenge for FX brokers</h3>
          <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed">
            You win clients on rate — but retaining them means offering more than execution. SME clients increasingly want cash visibility, exposure tracking, hedging guidance, and integration with their accounting systems. Building that technology stack from scratch takes years and millions. Without it, you compete purely on margin — a race to the bottom.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Solution -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Opportunity</p>
          <h3 class="text-[1.5rem] md:text-[1.75rem] font-bold text-text-heading mb-4 leading-tight">
            Extend your reach into the SME segment — without the build cost
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
            HedgeFlows gives your SME clients the treasury capabilities they need — cash management, FX risk monitoring, hedging guidance, payment automation, and accounting integrations — delivered through a platform built for businesses that don't have a treasury team. You keep the client relationship. We provide the infrastructure and advisory expertise.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Institutional-grade tools sized for SMEs and mid-market',
              'FX risk advisory backed by 40+ years of banking experience',
              'Multi-currency cash management and payment automation',
              'ERP and accounting integrations out of the box',
              'FCA-regulated with safeguarded client funds',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/assets/images/platform/fx-risk-hero.png" alt="Treasury platform for SME clients" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partnership Models -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[#F8FAFB]">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Partnership models</h2>
        <p class="section-subheading mx-auto">Flexible structures designed around how you want to work with us</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {partnerModels.map((model) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-8 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-green-pale flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={model.icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[1.125rem] font-bold text-text-heading mb-3">{model.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">{model.description}</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2.5 mt-auto">
              {model.features.map((f) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[0.875rem] text-text-body">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>{f}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/assets/images/platform/cashflow-plan.png" alt="Partner onboarding process" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">How It Works</p>
          <h3 class="text-[1.5rem] md:text-[1.75rem] font-bold text-text-heading mb-4 leading-tight">
            From conversation to client coverage in weeks
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We move fast. Most partnerships go from first conversation to live clients in under a month. Here's how it typically works:
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            {[
              { step: '1', title: 'Discovery call', description: 'We understand your client base, your current SME offering, and where the gaps are.' },
              { step: '2', title: 'Solution design', description: 'We design the partnership model — referral, embedded, or advisory collaboration — and agree commercial terms.' },
              { step: '3', title: 'Integration & training', description: 'Technical integration (if needed), team training, and co-branded materials. We get your relationship managers comfortable with the offering.' },
              { step: '4', title: 'Go live', description: 'Start introducing clients. We handle onboarding, treasury advisory, and ongoing support. You earn revenue and deepen client relationships.' },
            ].map((s) => (
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-green text-white flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-[0.875rem] font-bold">
                  {s.step}
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold text-text-heading mb-1">{s.title}</p>
                  <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed">{s.description}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Partner -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[#F8FAFB]">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Why financial institutions partner with us</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {whyPartner.map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-8 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-green-pale flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={item.icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[1.125rem] font-bold text-text-heading mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed">{item.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    headline="Let's explore how we can serve your SME clients together"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Explore a Partnership', href: '/treasury-health-check' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'Email partners@hedgeflows.com', href: 'mailto:partners@hedgeflows.com' }}
  />
</PageLayout>
